'''M19''' is a Russian multigaming eSports organization formed by acquiring the roster of [[Albus NoX Luna]] in January 2017. The organization using a brand name of the computer club and same name eSports organization formed in 1999 and disbanded all their rosters in 2005.

==History==

=== 2017 Season ===
The team acquired the roster of [[Albus NoX Luna]] at the start of the season and will participate in the [[LCL/2017_Season/Spring_Season|2017 LCL Spring Split]].

